Wa kabila da Simeoni, wanhu kumi na mbili elufu wahawapetigwa, wanhu kumi na mbili elufu wahawapetigwa, na wa kabila da Lawi, wanhu kumi na mbili elufu wahawapetigwa, na wa kabila da Isakali, wanhu kumi na mbili elufu wahawapetigwa,
